<HTML>

<HEAD>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="HTML Assistant Pro">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Jane Powers">
<META NAME="OPERATOR" CONTENT="Ernest Pang">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<CENTER>
<H1>REGULATION XV </H1>

<H2>TRIP REDUCTION/INDIRECT SOURCE</H2>
</CENTER> 

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="/rules/doc/r1501.doc"><IMG SRC="/icon/word.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></A><A HREF="r1501.html">Rule 1501 </A> - 
<B>Work Trip Reduction Plans</B> <BR> <UL><UL><UL><I>(Repealed December 8, 1995)</I></UL></UL></UL>

<LI><A HREF="/rules/doc/r1501-1.doc"><IMG SRC="/icon/word.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></A><A HREF="r1501-1.html">Rule 1501.1 </A> - 
<B>Alternatives to Work Trip Reduction Plans</B>  <BR><UL><UL><UL><I>(Repealed December 8, 1995)</I></UL></UL></UL>

<LI><A HREF="/rules/doc/r1502.doc"><IMG SRC="/icon/word.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></A><A HREF="r1502.html">Rule 1502 </A> - <B>District
Delegation to Local Governments</B><BR><UL><UL><UL><I> (Adopted February 12, 1993)</I></UL></UL></UL>

