<P> <LI> GRAMS OF VOC PER LITER OF MATERIAL is the weight of VOC per volume of material (ink, coating or adhesive) which is calculated by the following equation:
<P>
<IMG SRC="r1130-13.gif" WIDTH = 357 HEIGHT = 47 ALT="Undisplayed Graphic">

<TABLE >
<TR>
<TD VALIGN=top >
