<P><CENTER><B>APPENDIX B
<BR>MODELING ANALYSIS FOR VISIBILITY</B></CENTER>
<P>(a) The modeling analysis performed by the applicant shall consider:
<OL><LI> the net emission increase from the new or modified source; and
<P><LI> the location of the source and its distance to the closest boundary of specified Federal Class I area(s).</OL>
<P>(b) Level 1 and 2 screening analysis for adverse plume impact pursuant to subparagraph (b)(5)(C) of this rule for modeling analysis of plume visibility shall consider the following applicable screening background visual ranges:
