<TITLE>BOARD MEETING DATE:  December 13, 1996 AGENDA NO. 20   </TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY><P><IMG SRC="/icon/logo.gif" HEIGHT=75 WIDTH=56 ALIGN="LEFT">
