<BR>
(Amended January 8, 1982)(Rescinded March 6, 1992)
<P>
<B>RULE 107. DETERMINATION OF VOLATILE ORGANIC COMPOUNDS
IN ORGANIC MATERIAL</B>
<P>
Rescinded by the South Coast Air Quality Management District Board
at its March 6, 1992 Board meeting.
