<HTML>

<HEAD>

<TITLE>RULE 101 - Title</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.00">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Pat Wong">
<META NAME="OPERATOR" CONTENT="Pat Wong">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
(Adopted February 4, 1977)(Amended April 1, 1977)
<P>
<B>RULE 101. TITLE</B>
<P>
 These rules and regulations shall be known as the rules of the
South Coast Air Quality Management District.
</BODY>

</HTML>
