<HEAD>

<TITLE>RULE 104 -  Reporting of Source Test Data and Analyses</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.00">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Pat Wong">
<META NAME="OPERATOR" CONTENT="Pat Wong">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
(Adopted January 9, 1976)
<P>
<B>RULE 104.  REPORTING OF SOURCE TEST DATA AND ANALYSES</B>
<P>
 Source tests to determine compliance with the provisions of these
rules shall be conducted in accordance with the methods adopted
by the District or any method determined by the Air Pollution
Control Officer to be equivalent.  Results of all tests and analyses
shall be calculated to and reported at standard conditions.
</BODY>

</HTML>
<P>

