<TITLE>RULE 207. Altering or Falsifying of Permit</TITLE>
<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Rezvan Ramezani">
<META NAME="OPERATOR" CONTENT="Rezvan Ramezani">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
(Adopted January 9, 1976)
<P>
<B>RULE 207. ALTERING OR FALSIFYING OF PERMIT</B>
<P>
 A person shall not willfully deface, alter, forge, or falsify
any permit issued under these rules.
</BODY>

