<HEAD>
<TITLE>RULE 208. Permit for Open Burning</TITLE>
<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Rezvan Ramezani">
<META NAME="OPERATOR" CONTENT="Rezvan Ramezani">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
 (Adopted October 8, 1976)(Amended January 5, 1990)
<P>
 
<P>
<B>RULE 208. PERMIT FOR OPEN BURNING</B>
<P>
 A person, required to obtain a permit for open burning pursuant
to Rule 444, shall not set or allow any open outdoor fire without
first having applied for and been issued a written permit for
such fire by the Executive Officer.
</BODY>

</HTML>
