<P>
<B>RULE 1129. AEROSOL COATINGS</B>
<P>
Rescinded by the South Coast Air Quality Management District Board
on March 8, 1996 in accordance with the adoption of the Aerosol
Coating Products Regulation by the California Air Resources Board
on March 23, 1995. 
</BODY>

